OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,FA Belfast swim school has suddenly
OL,7,Fclosed leaving parents out of pocket
OL,8,Fand children without swim lessons.
OL,10,FJEM Swim School sent an email to
OL,11,Fparents last week informing them of
OL,12,Fthe closure, but gave no explanation
OL,13,For details regarding refunds.
OL,15,FUTV approached JEM Swim School for
OL,16,Fcomment but received no response.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
