PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776780668
OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,FUTV were contacted by parents whose
OL,7,Fchildren attended swim classes ran by
OL,8,FJEM Swim School.JThe company sent an
OL,9,Femail, seen by UTV, to parents on
OL,10,FApril 13 to inform them of their
OL,11,Fimmmediate closure.
OL,13,FThey thanked parents for their support
OL,14,Fbut provided no written apology or
OL,15,Fexplanation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776780668
OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,FMany parents including Christine
OL,7,FFleming were left feeling let down and
OL,8,Ffrustrated.J"Everyone's angry. There
OL,9,Fhasn't really been much of an
OL,10,Fexplanation. It was very basic`'we are
OL,11,Fnow closed'.
OL,13,F"No apology, no offer of refund, or no
OL,14,Fexplanation as to why they couldn't
OL,15,Frefund," she said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776780668
OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,F"I think a lot of people are annoyed,
OL,7,Fmainly more around the kids now having
OL,8,Fto restart again, trying to find
OL,9,Fanother swim school that they can go
OL,10,Fto, when they've built up
OL,11,Frelationships with these teachers.
OL,13,F"My son's been going for over a year
OL,14,Fnow, so he's used to everyone there,
OL,15,Fand I don't know if it would be the
OL,16,Fsame if he moved somewhere else," Ms
OL,17,FFleming added.
OL,19,FMany parents block booked lessons and
OL,20,Fpaid up-front however there was no
OL,21,Fmention in the email regarding refunds.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776780668
OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,FSarah Cully was another parent left
OL,7,Fsignificantly out of pocket.
OL,9,FShe said: "We were told it would be
OL,10,Fadvisable to pay cash, which`that's
OL,11,Ffine. Both children we paid`one was
OL,12,Ffor eight weeks, the other was for
OL,13,Fnine weeks. So it was, say, #150 each,
OL,14,Fand we're still owed... five lessons
OL,15,Feach for each child, so that works out
OL,16,Fover 100 pounds still we're owed."
OL,18,FUTV contacted JEM Swim School via
OL,19,Femail and telephone for a response but
OL,20,Freceived no reply.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
