OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776780668
OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,FThey either deleted or suspended their
OL,7,Fsocial media accounts and their
OL,8,Fwebsite is "currently unavailable".
OL,10,FMethodist College Belfast, rented out
OL,11,Ftheir pool to the swim school but told
OL,12,FUTV they also tried to contact them
OL,13,Fbut received no response.
OL,15,FJEM Swimming Limited is still listed
OL,16,Fas trading on the Companies House
OL,17,Fwebsite.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
