OL,3,CAnger as parents left out of pocket
OL,4,Cover JEM Swim School closure
OL,6,FCompanies House told UTV, a process
OL,7,Fwould be required for JEM Swim School
OL,8,Fto cease trading but that has not been
OL,9,Fstarted.
